    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand mb-4">SEO Pricing in Swansea</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">SEO pricing in Swansea is more accessible than most Welsh business owners expect. Monthly retainers for professional search engine optimisation start from £497 per month for small businesses and scale to £1,997 per month for enterprise-level campaigns. Unlike agencies in Cardiff or Bristol that inflate costs with unnecessary overheads, Swansea-based SEO delivers strong ROI at a fraction of the price because local keyword competition is lower, and proximity to the businesses we serve means faster, more responsive work.</p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">This page breaks down exactly what you get at each price point, what one-off services cost, and how to calculate whether SEO is a profitable investment for your specific business. No vague quotes, no hidden fees, no surprises on the invoice.</p>

    <div class="bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400 p-4 rounded-r-lg my-6">
      <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-1">Quick Answer</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700">SEO in Swansea costs between £497 and £1,997 per month depending on the number of keywords, content requirements, and competition level. One-off audits start from £297. All plans are rolling monthly with no lock-in contracts. Most businesses see measurable results within 3-4 months.</p>
