    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Why Transparent Pricing Matters</h2>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">The SEO industry has a reputation problem. Too many agencies hide behind "bespoke quotes" and "it depends" answers because they want to charge as much as each client will tolerate. That approach benefits the agency, not the business owner.</p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Transparent pricing does three things. First, it lets you budget accurately before the first conversation. Second, it forces the agency to define exactly what you receive for your money. Third, it builds trust because there is nothing to hide. A restaurant on <strong>Mumbles seafront</strong> and a tradesman operating from <strong>Morriston</strong> have different budgets and different needs. Transparent tiers let each choose the right level of investment without pressure.</p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">We publish our prices because we are confident in the value they represent. Every deliverable listed below is something we actually do each month, not a line item padded to justify the fee. If you want to compare us against other providers, you will find our <a href="/services/" class="text-brand hover:underline">full service descriptions</a> equally transparent.</p>

