    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Not every business needs a monthly retainer. These standalone services give you expert insight without ongoing commitment. Each one delivers a detailed report with prioritised actions you can implement yourself or hand to your developer.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 my-8">
      <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow text-center">
