    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">The difference is driven by three factors. Bristol agencies carry higher office rents and salary costs. Cardiff has a larger pool of competing agencies, which paradoxically drives prices up as agencies invest more in their own marketing. Swansea offers lower overheads and a business community where relationships are built on results rather than corporate polish.</p>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Critically, lower pricing does not mean lower quality. The same Google algorithm applies in SA1 as it does in CF10 or BS1. The technical work, content strategy, and link building methodology are identical. Swansea businesses simply pay less for the same calibre of work because the agency delivering it operates more efficiently.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">What Affects SEO Pricing</h2>

    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Not every business needs the same level of investment. These six factors determine where your business sits on the pricing scale.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">Competition Level</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">A solicitor competing for "personal injury claims Swansea" faces far more SEO competition than a dog groomer targeting "dog grooming Mumbles." Higher competition means more content, more links, and more technical refinement to rank, which increases the monthly investment required.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">Number of Keywords</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Each keyword target requires dedicated on-page optimisation, content creation, and performance tracking. Five keywords on the Starter plan is manageable for a focused local business. A company serving multiple areas across South Wales or targeting national terms will need the Growth or Enterprise plan to cover 15 to 30 or more keywords effectively.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">Current Website Condition</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">A well-built website with clean code, fast loading speeds, and proper structure needs less upfront <a href="/technical-seo-swansea/" class="text-brand hover:underline">technical SEO</a> work. A site built on an outdated platform with broken links, missing meta data, and no mobile optimisation may require an initial technical overhaul before monthly SEO work can gain traction. Our <a href="/seo-audit-swansea/" class="text-brand hover:underline">SEO audit</a> identifies exactly where your site stands.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">Content Requirements</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Some industries require substantial content production to establish topical authority. A business operating near <strong>Swansea Enterprise Park</strong> in the B2B sector may need detailed case studies, whitepapers, and industry guides. A local cafe needs Google Business Profile posts and location-page optimisation. The content workload directly influences pricing tier selection.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">Geographic Scope</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Targeting "plumber Swansea" is a single-location campaign. Targeting plumbing services across Swansea, Neath Port Talbot, Carmarthenshire, and Pembrokeshire requires location-specific pages, separate Google Business Profile management, and broader link building. Multi-location campaigns typically sit in the Growth or Enterprise tier.</p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-8 mb-3">AI Search Readiness</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">Google AI Overviews, ChatGPT search, and Perplexity are reshaping how customers find local businesses. Optimising for these platforms requires structured data, entity-based content, and citation strategies that go beyond traditional SEO. Our <a href="/ai-search-optimisation-swansea/" class="text-brand hover:underline">AI search optimisation</a> service addresses this directly, and it is included in all monthly plans at the appropriate level.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-12 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <div class="space-y-2 my-6">
