        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 py-2 px-4">How much does SEO cost in Swansea?</summary>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">SEO in Swansea typically costs between £497 and £1,997 per month depending on the scope of work, number of keyword targets, and level of competition in your industry. One-off audits start from £297. These prices are 20-40% lower than equivalent services in Cardiff or Bristol due to lower agency overheads in Swansea.</p>
      </details>

      <details class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-medium text-gray-900 py-2 px-4">Why is SEO cheaper in Swansea than Cardiff or Bristol?</summary>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed px-4 pb-4">Swansea has lower agency overheads and less keyword competition than Cardiff or Bristol. Office space, salaries, and operating costs are all lower, which translates directly to lower fees without compromising on the quality of work. The same Google ranking factors apply everywhere, so Swansea businesses get the same methodology at a better price point.</p>
